    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《浮岛工厂》是一款将塔防和全自动流水线结合的地牢爬行游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/9822468898a7a0ec8aa8df0fee5a2a34.poster.avif?t=1750260125\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/9822468898a7a0ec8aa8df0fee5a2a34.webm?t=1750260125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/9822468898a7a0ec8aa8df0fee5a2a34.mp4?t=1750260125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造一个相互连接的流水线工厂，扩大生产规模，购买岛屿，制作新的怪物孵化器等等。从新敌人那里获取新材料，以用于建造全新的物品来升级你的装配线，提升工厂的供应效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/2037e591cbb530d7f3b48230aa5864ed.poster.avif?t=1750260125\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/2037e591cbb530d7f3b48230aa5864ed.webm?t=1750260125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/2037e591cbb530d7f3b48230aa5864ed.mp4?t=1750260125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败一波又一波敌人，把他们变成工厂的原材料，并通过建造城墙或其他建筑，改变敌人的行进路线，最大化伤害输出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/24fae76d6b777fbbc77a9b410159cda8.poster.avif?t=1750260125\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/24fae76d6b777fbbc77a9b410159cda8.webm?t=1750260125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182630/extras/24fae76d6b777fbbc77a9b410159cda8.mp4?t=1750260125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用敌人掉落的资源制作药水。巫师梅尔文将使用这些资源升级的你工厂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用资源购买新的岛屿，这些岛屿上会有全新的怪物孵化器、资源类型，以及扩大流水线所需的土地。</p>",
